？<br />\n例如有巴打提議過，將凍飲杯蓋，改用熱飲杯蓋嗰種設計，開一個口出嚟，飲嗰陣就可以頂住啲冰，又可以走飲筒<br />\n<br />\n今次走飲筒事件只係導火線，真正成因係對嗰一味走呢樣走嗰樣，走到痴曬線嘅環保撚宣洩不滿"},{"pid":"fe011e79d5325180482784b64c65cf4a95f748e6","tid":967640,"uid":205462,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T16:50:52.000Z","msg":"如果係因為海洋生物誤吞膠製品，唔係應該先檢控亂拋垃圾落海嘅船家咩?<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港嘅三色回收箱，裡面嘅膠類回收物，當中大部份都係掉去堆填區㗎啦，政府唔係想誤導市民呀?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffefcce2825e01acb8fa1d626469eab3e68028a4","tid":967640,"uid":1724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T16:51:42.000Z","msg":"敏感牙齒<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e80b9bcfbd252f638eb2fdc080b6018b6030f5d0","tid":967640,"uid":153496,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T16:53:47.000Z","msg":"拎支飲管好似殺咗樓主咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fe8b13a81ba7aa4add7885fe55cc45f286aa70e","tid":967640,"uid":201374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T16:54:24.000Z","msg":"我相信每年俾人食落肚嘅海洋生物絕對比因為飲管插落個鼻而死嘅多<br />\n有辦法走晒漁業先嚟講走飲管ok? <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4d8fe7848983fe5c43df5e4576853ed588b2e76","tid":967640,"uid":78683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fa8438e6fd2ecced6dd6eacddb7fefaf1105622b","tid":967640,"uid":42659,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"298e76de47987bfbbe5964f4b0dec26bf984ded8","tid":967640,"uid":78683,"like":4,"dislike":13,"score":-9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T16:14:52.000Z","msg":"地球無咗呢種生物唔會有影響"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T16:21:18.000Z","msg":"咁地球無左你都唔會有影響喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T05:58:28.000Z","msg":"你同我喺地球都只係一粒塵 我亦都唔覺得我死咗會對地球有影響<br />\n無論你在世嘅時候有幾多功績<br />\n死咗都只係會畀人憑弔 <br 